<P>
ROUNDUP; EDISON ROUTS MARINA IN SUNSET MEET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Sophomores Kelly Marshall, Marie Philman and Kerry O'Bric led Edison to a 
102-25 victory over Marina in a Sunset League girls' track and field meet 
Thursday at Edison. 
</P>
<P>
 Marshall won the 200, the 400 and ran the anchor legs on the 400 and 1,600 
relay teams. Philman won the 100 hurdles, the high jump, the shot put and the 
discus. O'Bric took first in the 300 hurdles, the long jump and the triple jump 
for Edison (6-0, 4-0 in league). 
</P>
<P>
 In another Sunset League meet: 
</P>
