<P>
ESCAMILLA, COLLINS, SEBEK HONORED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Mark Sebek of Nordhoff High, Jason Collins of Harvard-Westlake and Manuel 
Escamilla of Santa Paula have been selected to the All-Southern Section 
Division III basketball first team by the Amateur Athletic Foundation. 
</P>
<P>
 Selected to the second team were Micah Hanson of Moorpark, Scott Garson of 
Harvard-Westlake, John George of Littlerock and Braden Weber of St. Francis. 
</P>
<P>
 Selected to the All-Southern Section Division IV first team were Damian 
Cantrell of Santa Clara, Shawn Williams of Oak Park and David Gustafson of 
Village Christian. 
</P>
<P>
 The second team included Chad Hanson of Village Christian, Damien Smith of 
Santa Clara, Rod Tepesano of St. Bonaventure, Brandon Creason of Oak Park and 
Landon LaPack of L.A. Baptist. 
</P>
