<TEXT>
<P>
 A robbery in Northridge left two brothers dead and two of three suspects in 
custody, including one who was accidentally wounded by a gunman who escaped, 
police said Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
 The attack occurred at 8:15 p.m. Wednesday in the 8600 block of Wilbur Avenue, 
