<P>
 The League of Women Voters of Orange County will hold a free educational forum 
on the various health care reform proposals Wednesday at the Richard Nixon 
Library & Birthplace. 
</P>
<P>
 The forum, "Citizens' Voice for Citizens' Choice: A Campaign for a Public 
