<TEXT>
<P>
 No. 1 in the Land: When asked what the leading real estate sales organization 
is, Century 21 got the largest share of votes -- 32% -- from homeowners, 
according to an independent study. 
</P>
<P>
 In addition, 99% of 1,800 homeowners questioned in a recent national telephone 
survey conducted by the Wirthlin Group (in McLean, Va.), recognized the Century 
21 name. 
</P>
<P>
 Based in Irvine, Century 21 Real Estate Corp. is the world's largest real 
estate sales organization with operations in 15 countries and territories and 
about 6,000 independently owned and operated franchised broker offices. 
</P>
<P>
 "The latest survey results are stronger in virtually every consumer preference 
and image category and clearly show the strength of the Century 21 image," said 
Hal George, vice president of research for Century 21.  
</P>
<P>
 The 1994 National Survey of Homeowners was conducted during the first two 
weeks of January by Wirthlin. 
