homers and 57 RBIs. 
</P>
<P>
 With the Angels: 10,06,04,04,04,04,04,04,04,05,04 AVG G AB R H 2B 3B HR RBI SB 
.280 25 75 9 21 5 0 1 13 1 MISCELLANY: Named Sun Belt Conference player of the 
